			"type": "action",
			"name": "Twin Feint",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The Butterfly Blade's uses an attack with one weapon to distract their foe from a second attack coming at a different angle. They Make one Strike with each of their two melee weapons, both against the same target. The target is automatically @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Off-Guard} against the second attack. Apply their multiple attack penalty to the Strikes normally.</p><p>If both the Butterfly Blade's Strikes deal damage to a targeted creature, the target must succeed at a @Check[will|dc:31] saving throw or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 1} until the end of their next turn.</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
